{"tid":2512871,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人俾轉生蜘蛛人類線搞到唔敢推薦俾朋友睇","createTime":"2021-05-02T05:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:21:07.000Z","uid":200529,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1271a21230e4e3b6db92c0638d207410dbdf12","tid":2512871,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"事緣套野係分蜘蛛線同人類線，雙線發展我冇咩意見，但正因為雙線發展，兩條線嘅時間差唔多，人類線真係唔應該整到咁差<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛線非常多笑點，蜘蛛子豐富嘅表情動作，悠木碧完美演釋，第12集強者對決，由頭打到尾，勁精彩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cVPa4N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cVPa4N.png&h=121909d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwBuVws.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwBuVws.png&h=4e227556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人類線就偏悶，第一季就除咗第三集超離譜嘅ppt打鬥，我個人都接受到，畢竟係為後面劇情鋪排，但第二季人類線戲肉真係整到勁差，應該緊張嘅劇情俾作畫分鏡搞到燥，十年前嘅h動都唔知搵唔搵到咁差<br />\n<br />\n唔知打緊乜，人物各種崩<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTy6Wv4Ff31kexq8YtpF1kegMrbjytQNDApSZRddF7Nio?filename=c4NenjP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4NenjP.png&h=b4cb0326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33h2wc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33h2wc9.png&h=f086dfb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全唔養眼甚至傷眼嘅泳裝環節，原本啲女幾靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YRnwc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YRnwc8.png&h=e1f75815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ce8QE6u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fce8QE6u.png&h=a15ed72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勁失望，可唔可以重製人類線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0827031eb7abbaafee246578a49b6fc045954b","tid":2512871,"uid":139173,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"人類線WFC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634e5c74cc8d4d5ed80a80b0723afd06637902e7","tid":2512871,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c0827031eb7abbaafee246578a49b6fc045954b","tid":2512871,"uid":139173,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"人類線WFC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"連魔王都崩過 唔知幾時會到gg子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b2e0cf9c5c4faa4a08057e256ef4032fd34779","tid":2512871,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"真心鍾意依套 但製作一啖糖一啖屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20baec68a4c4fecb83deb65d7860b322be2ec673","tid":2512871,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知會唔會做到 gg子人類化會唔會崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63d31355f813f269c95f44c7388b319ae495c56","tid":2512871,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"難怪要殺哂人類"},{"pid":"30b647abaffd4229128f931cdc5023c33bb87abc","tid":2512871,"uid":271975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"人類線飛左8成...好悶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc45591759ac0c7dcb46bdc1b3afc415f80de0a9","tid":2512871,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b647abaffd4229128f931cdc5023c33bb87abc","tid":2512871,"uid":271975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"人類線飛左8成...好悶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"最